{SOUTH has one of those hands which might or might not be helpful to NORTH. He needs 
more information about NORTH's hand, so he bids 2NT.

NORTH has a better than average hand, so she bids 3\C to show a high card in the suit.

SOUTH was hoping for a high card in \Ds rather than \Cs, so 
he signs off in 3\S}

